You're still set on that? 你仍然坚持你的想法吗？
If you're set on divorce, I can help you with that. 如果你决心要离婚，我可以帮你。
I never really had my heart set on being a novelist. 我从来就没有决心当一个小说家。
I wanted to marry you the first time I set eyes on you. 我在第一眼见到你的时候，就决心一定要娶你。
Why doesn't she become a doctor? 她为什么没成为一个医生？
Because she is set on becoming a lawyer instead. 因为她决心当一个律师。